    "description": "Creema Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, operates as an online marketplace where individuals can directly buy and sell original handmade works online in Japan and internationally. It offers products in accessories and jewelry, fashion, bags, wallets, cases, and small organizers, iPhone cases, smartphones, PCs, furniture, interior goods and household items, art, tableware and kitchen, plush toys and ornaments, miscellaneous goods and stationery, pet goods, baby and kids, wedding, men's, handmade materials, food, alcohol, and drinks categories. The company also provides pearl, cotton pearl, leather, skin leather, yarn, felt, wool, canvas, brass, glass, stained glass, silver, natural stone, and other material products. In addition, the company offers platform services, such as marketing support; crowdfunding services; gift catalog services; and creator empowerment services, as well as operates an EC platform site that sells artists' works and videos, and a lesson video platform; and organizes events. Creema Ltd. was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
